properties.name: Home to Top of Brown Mtn via Gould, Fern Truck, Ken Burton 18
properties.description: Long route from home up Angeles Crest and down to Gould Campground.  From there hang a left on Gabriellino to the waterfall, ascent Fern Truck and Ken Burton to top of Brown Mtn.  Distance (mi): 17.83, Ascent (ft): 4590, Peak Ele (ft): 4470
